Former Big Brother Naija house, Tega Dominic, has urged her fans and Nigerians to be careful of the partner they choose to have a child with. The BBN star disclosed this on Sunday in a story via her Instagram page, expressing that one might be digging their grave by having a child for the wrong partner. She said, “Be careful who you have a child with, you may be digging your grave! -Advertisement- “At this point I don’t even mean who you marry, I mean who you have a child with.”